Package nachogame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackGround
    This class set the background image according to the game panel size.
    Enemy
    This is a Enemy class for the space nacho game.
    Entity
    Each entity represent an element in the game, the entity is responsible for element's position and resolve image.
    Logic
    This is the game engine for our space nachos game.
    NachoPanel
    This is the panel where all the action happens for our awesome space nachos game.
    Projectile
    This is a Projectile class for spaceNachos.
    Scaler
    This class is used for scaling space objects.
    Ship
    This is the ship class which inherits from space object nacho game.
    SpaceObject
    This class creates object for the game which enemy, ship and enemy inherit from.
    Table
    This is the table class that sets the image of the table and determines if the nacho reaches the table without correct sauce apply to the nacho.
    TacoBoss
    This is a TacoBoss class which inherits from enemy for the space nacho game.
